law.history: Repealed 1966 Ky. Acts ch. 254, sec. 11, effective July 1, 1971. -- Amended 1966 Ky. Acts ch. 254, sec. 5, effective July 1, 1966. -- Amended 1956 Ky. Acts ch. 114, sec. 1. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. secs. 4214a-13, 4214a-16, 4221a-17.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Tax on manufacturing and importation of distilled spirits -- Biennial reduction -- Exemption of non beverage alcohol.
